<p>
RAJIV GANDHI COLLEGE OF ENGINEERING AND TECHNOLOGY, an institution of academic excellence, 
was
established in the year
1999, with a cherished desire to serve the cause of humanity through technical higher
education. 
This college has
been affiliated to Pondicherry University, Chennai and has been recognized by the 
Government of
PUDUCHERRY. It is a
Co-Educational Engineering College offering  B.Tech., courses and 
P.G.
courses. All the courses have
been recognized by the All India Council for Technical Education, New Delhi.
